<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="tr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Hakkımızda - Zaman Çizelgesi</title>
    <style>
        body {
        font-family: 'San Francisco', 'Helvetica Neue', 'Segoe UI', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        line-height: 1.5;
        }

        .container {
        padding: 2rem;
        padding-bottom: 400px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        max-width: 800px;
        overflow: hidden;
        }

        .top-section {
        text-align: center;
        padding: 4rem 0;
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .timeline {
        position: relative;
        min-height: 150px;
        }

        .timeline__line {
        position: absolute;
        z-index: 2;
        left: calc(50% - 1px);
        width: 2px;
        top: -50px;
        bottom: -50px;
        background-color: #000;
        display: none;
        }

        .timeline__line:before,
        .timeline__line:after {
        position: absolute;
        display: block;
        content: '';
        height: 1rem;
        width: 1rem;
        border-radius: 50%;
        background-color: #000;
        left: 50%;
        transform: translateX(-50%);
        }

        .timeline__line:after {
        bottom: 0;
        }

        .timeline__section {
        display: flex;
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translatex(-100%);
        transition: 600ms ease;
        position: relative;
        z-index: 1;
        margin: 50px 0;
        padding: 1rem;
        border-radius: 1rem;
        align-items: center;
        min-height: 300px;
        }

        .timeline__section:nth-child(odd) {
        flex-direction: row-reverse;
        transform: translatex(100%);
        }

        .timeline__section__bead {
        position: absolute;
        display: block;
        height: 1rem;
        width: 1rem;
        border-radius: 50%;
        background-color: #000;
        left: 50%;
        top: 20%;
        transform: translateX(-50%);
        }

        .timeline__section__content {
        width: calc(50% - 2rem);
        }

        .show-me:nth-child(n) {
        transform: none;
        opacity: 1;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="container">
    <div class="top-section">
        <h1>Animated timeline</h1>
        <p>Lorem ipsum dolor, sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Quam accusantium cumque quos, aperiam nostrum quod reiciendis illum fugit beatae, nisi, nulla laboriosam! Officia tenetur iusto quis dolorem repudiandae inventore reiciendis.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="timeline">
        <div class="timeline__line"></div>

        <div class="timeline__section">
        <div class="timeline__section__bead"></div>
        <div class="timeline__section__content">
            <h2>İnovasyon</h2>
            <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Aut enim sunt modi qui cum eveniet magni iure laudantium vitae. At corporis sequi porro doloremque obcaecati repudiandae nemo? Delectus, praesentium fuga?</p>
        </div>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline__section">
        <div class="timeline__section__bead"></div>
        <div class="timeline__section__content">
            <h2>Güven</h2>
            <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Aut enim sunt modi qui cum eveniet magni iure laudantium vitae. At corporis sequi porro doloremque obcaecati repudiandae nemo? Delectus, praesentium fuga?</p>
        </div>
